{
  "video_id": "ndsB37KUAso",
  "title": "The anatomy of melancholy -- Can depression be good for you? | Neel Burton | TEDxMaribor",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 4342.0,
      "end_time": 6424.0,
      "text": "Hello everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 6424.0,
      "end_time": 10190.0,
      "text": "I mostly live in an attic in Oxford,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10190.0,
      "end_time": 16349.0,
      "text": "so you&#39;ll forgive me for being completely outside my environment tonight."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 16349.0,
      "end_time": 19719.0,
      "text": "I&amp;#x27;m afraid I&amp;#x27;m not going to be terribly"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 19719.0,
      "end_time": 22570.0,
      "text": "funny like the previous speakers."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22570.0,
      "end_time": 26725.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s partly because psychiatrists aren&#39;t very funny people."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26725.0,
      "end_time": 31583.0,
      "text": "Freud famously said that there&#39;s no such thing as a joke."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31583.0,
      "end_time": 34211.0,
      "text": "But, no, actually it&amp;#x27;s because that"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34211.0,
      "end_time": 38860.0,
      "text": "my topic tonight doesn&#39;t lend itself very well to jokes"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38860.0,
      "end_time": 41334.0,
      "text": "and my topic is actually a very serious topic."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41334.0,
      "end_time": 43442.0,
      "text": "It&amp;#x27;s depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43442.0,
      "end_time": 45581.0,
      "text": "Now, most people think of depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45581.0,
      "end_time": 51862.0,
      "text": "as a mental disorder that is a biological illness of the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51862.0,
      "end_time": 55644.0,
      "text": "Today, I&#39;m going to argue that the concept of depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55644.0,
      "end_time": 59097.0,
      "text": "as a mental disorder has been over extended,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59097.0,
      "end_time": 61860.0,
      "text": "has been unhelpfully over extended to"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61860.0,
      "end_time": 66301.0,
      "text": "include all manner of human suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66301.0,
      "end_time": 68548.0,
      "text": "And, more controversially,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68548.0,
      "end_time": 75222.0,
      "text": "that depression or &quot;depression&quot; as broadly understood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75222.0,
      "end_time": 78057.0,
      "text": "can actually be good for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78057.0,
      "end_time": 81391.0,
      "text": "an idea that I explored, that I developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81391.0,
      "end_time": 86099.0,
      "text": "in my recent book &quot;The Meaning of Madness.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86099.0,
      "end_time": 91022.0,
      "text": "Now let us begin by thinking very broadly about depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 91022.0,
      "end_time": 94424.0,
      "text": "There are important geographical variations"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 94424.0,
      "end_time": 99473.0,
      "text": "in the prevalence of depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 99473.0,
      "end_time": 102223.0,
      "text": "And these can in large part be accounted for"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 102223.0,
      "end_time": 107143.0,
      "text": "by socio-cultural rather than biological factors."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 107143.0,
      "end_time": 112477.0,
      "text": "In traditional societies, human distress is more likely to be seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 112477.0,
      "end_time": 117742.0,
      "text": "as an indicator of the need to address important life problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 117742.0,
      "end_time": 123862.0,
      "text": "than as a mental disorder requiring professional treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 123862.0,
      "end_time": 128725.0,
      "text": "For this reason, the diagnosis of depression is correspondingly"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 128725.0,
      "end_time": 131808.0,
      "text": "less common."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 131808.0,
      "end_time": 135856.0,
      "text": "Some linguistic communities do not have a word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 135856.0,
      "end_time": 140822.0,
      "text": "or even a concept with which to talk or think about depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 140822.0,
      "end_time": 143714.0,
      "text": "And many people in traditional societies"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 143714.0,
      "end_time": 146606.0,
      "text": "with what may be construed as depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 146606.0,
      "end_time": 149500.0,
      "text": "present instead with physical symptoms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 149500.0,
      "end_time": 154862.0,
      "text": "such as fatigue, or headache, or chest pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 154862.0,
      "end_time": 159821.0,
      "text": "So, for example, Punjabi women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 159821.0,
      "end_time": 164780.0,
      "text": "who have recently emigrated to the United Kingdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 164780.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "and given birth find it baffling"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170710.0,
      "text": "that a health visitor should pop around"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 170710.0,
      "end_time": 175221.0,
      "text": "to make sure that they haven&#39;t developed post-natal depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 175221.0,
      "end_time": 177533.0,
      "text": "I mean, not only had they never"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 177533.0,
      "end_time": 183469.0,
      "text": "conceived of giving birth as anything but a joyous event"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 183469.0,
      "end_time": 186589.0,
      "text": "but they don&amp;#x27;t even have a word"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 186589.0,
      "end_time": 194368.0,
      "text": "with which to translate the concept of depression into Punjabi."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 194368.0,
      "end_time": 198684.0,
      "text": "Now, in modern societies such as the UK and the USA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 198684.0,
      "end_time": 201465.0,
      "text": "people talk about depression very freely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 201465.0,
      "end_time": 203780.0,
      "text": "very readily, very openly."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 203780.0,
      "end_time": 207437.0,
      "text": "As a result, they are far more likely to interpret"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 207437.0,
      "end_time": 210347.0,
      "text": "their distress in terms of depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 210347.0,
      "end_time": 215622.0,
      "text": "and also far more likely to seek out a diagnosis of the illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 215622.0,
      "end_time": 218941.0,
      "text": "At the same time, groups with vested interests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 218941.0,
      "end_time": 221762.0,
      "text": "such as pharmaceutical companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 221762.0,
      "end_time": 225136.0,
      "text": "or indeed, so called mental health experts"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 225136.0,
      "end_time": 229188.0,
      "text": "promote the notion of &quot;saccharin happiness&quot; as a natural,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 229188.0,
      "end_time": 233194.0,
      "text": "default state and of human misery, of human distress"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 233194.0,
      "end_time": 237087.0,
      "text": "as a mental disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 237087.0,
      "end_time": 242450.0,
      "text": "The concept of depression as a mental disorder can be useful"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 242450.0,
      "end_time": 245702.0,
      "text": "for some of the more severe intractible cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 245702.0,
      "end_time": 248431.0,
      "text": "that are treated by hospital psychiatrists."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 248431.0,
      "end_time": 251989.0,
      "text": "But probably not for the vast majority of cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 251989.0,
      "end_time": 255822.0,
      "text": "which are relatively mild and short-lived"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 255822.0,
      "end_time": 259299.0,
      "text": "and easily understood in terms of life problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 259298.99999999997,
      "end_time": 264750.0,
      "text": "human nature or the human condition."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 264750.0,
      "end_time": 267625.0,
      "text": "Another non-mutually exclusive explanation"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 267625.0,
      "end_time": 270120.0,
      "text": "for the important geographical variations"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 270120.0,
      "end_time": 272585.0,
      "text": "in the prevalence of depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 272585.0,
      "end_time": 276864.0,
      "text": "may lie in the nature of modern societies themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 276864.0,
      "end_time": 280021.0,
      "text": "which have become increasingly individualistic"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 280021.0,
      "end_time": 283298.0,
      "text": "and divorced from traditional values."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 283298.0,
      "end_time": 287367.0,
      "text": "For many people living in our society today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 287367.0,
      "end_time": 292181.0,
      "text": "life can seem both suffocating and far removed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 292181.0,
      "end_time": 297182.0,
      "text": "lonely even and especially amongst the multitudes."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 297182.0,
      "end_time": 301890.0,
      "text": "And not only meaningless but absurd."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 301890.0,
      "end_time": 306381.0,
      "text": "By encoding their distress in terms of a mental disorder"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 306381.0,
      "end_time": 309152.0,
      "text": "our society may be subtly implying"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 309152.0,
      "end_time": 313699.0,
      "text": "that the problem lies not with itself, but with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 313699.0,
      "end_time": 318340.0,
      "text": "fragile and failing individuals that they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 318340.0,
      "end_time": 321861.0,
      "text": "Now, of course, many people prefer to buy into this"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 321861.0,
      "end_time": 325863.0,
      "text": "reductionist, physicalist explanation"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 325863.0,
      "end_time": 330500.0,
      "text": "rather than, I suppose, confront their existential angst."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 330500.0,
      "end_time": 334141.0,
      "text": "However, thinking of human distress in terms of"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 334141.0,
      "end_time": 337661.0,
      "text": "a mental disorder can  be counterproductive"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 337661.0,
      "end_time": 341951.0,
      "text": "because it can prevent people from identifying"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 341951.0,
      "end_time": 345656.0,
      "text": "and addressing the important psychological"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 345656.0,
      "end_time": 351742.0,
      "text": "or life problems that are at the root of their distress."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 351742.0,
      "end_time": 353635.0,
      "text": "Now, all of this is not to say that"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 353635.0,
      "end_time": 355528.0,
      "text": "the concept of depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 355528.0,
      "end_time": 357422.0,
      "text": "as a mental disorder is bogus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 357422.0,
      "end_time": 359412.0,
      "text": "not at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 359412.0,
      "end_time": 362342.0,
      "text": "but only that the diagnosis of depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 362342.0,
      "end_time": 364460.0,
      "text": "has been overextended"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 364460.0,
      "end_time": 367503.0,
      "text": "to include far more than just depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 367503.0,
      "end_time": 369662.0,
      "text": "the mental disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 369662.0,
      "end_time": 373480.0,
      "text": "If like the majority of medical conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 373480.0,
      "end_time": 377142.0,
      "text": "depression could be diagnosed according to its etiology"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 377142.0,
      "end_time": 381580.0,
      "text": "or pathology, that is, according to its cause or effect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 381580.0,
      "end_time": 383799.0,
      "text": "then such a situation, such a problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 383799.0,
      "end_time": 386328.0,
      "text": "would never have arisen."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 386328.0,
      "end_time": 389413.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, depression cannot as yet be diagnosed"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 389413.0,
      "end_time": 392451.0,
      "text": "according ot its etiology or pathology"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 392451.0,
      "end_time": 399032.0,
      "text": "but only according to its clinical manifestations or symptoms."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 399032.0,
      "end_time": 404379.0,
      "text": "Given this, a doctor cannot base a diagnosis"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 404379.0,
      "end_time": 409453.0,
      "text": "of depression on anything so objective as for example"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 409453.0,
      "end_time": 411653.0,
      "text": "a blood test as in malaria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 411653.0,
      "end_time": 414493.0,
      "text": "or a brain scan as in stroke"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 414493.0,
      "end_time": 417533.0,
      "text": "but only on his subjective interpretation"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 417533.0,
      "end_time": 422972.0,
      "text": "of the nature and severity of the patient&#39;s symptoms."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 422972.0,
      "end_time": 425693.0,
      "text": "If some of these symptoms happen to tally with"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 425693.0,
      "end_time": 428092.0,
      "text": "a diagnostic criteria for depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 428092.0,
      "end_time": 431814.0,
      "text": "then, you know, bingo, the doctor is justified"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 431814.0,
      "end_time": 435536.0,
      "text": "in making a diagnosis of depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 435536.0,
      "end_time": 437345.0,
      "text": "Now, the problem here"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 437345.0,
      "end_time": 441558.0,
      "text": "is that the definition of depression is circular,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 441558.0,
      "end_time": 443911.0,
      "text": "the concept of depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 443911.0,
      "end_time": 446891.0,
      "text": "is based on the symptoms of depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 446891.0,
      "end_time": 449336.0,
      "text": "and the symptoms of depression, in turn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 449336.0,
      "end_time": 453079.0,
      "text": "are based on the concept of depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 453079.0,
      "end_time": 455448.0,
      "text": "Thus, it is impossible to be certain"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 455448.0,
      "end_time": 457502.0,
      "text": "that the concept of depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 457502.0,
      "end_time": 466928.0,
      "text": "maps onto any distinct disease entity."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 466928.0,
      "end_time": 469591.0,
      "text": "And, particularly since a diagnosis of depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 469591.0,
      "end_time": 474972.0,
      "text": "can apply to anything from mild depression to depressive psychosis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 474972.0,
      "end_time": 476908.0,
      "text": "and depressive stupor"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 476908.0,
      "end_time": 480614.0,
      "text": "and overlap with a number of other mental disorders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 480614.0,
      "end_time": 484015.0,
      "text": "including anxiety disorders, dysthymia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 484015.0,
      "end_time": 487384.0,
      "text": "and adjustment disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 487384.0,
      "end_time": 490963.0,
      "text": "One of the consequences of our many of symptoms approach"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 490963.0,
      "end_time": 494531.0,
      "text": "to diagnosing depression is that two people"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 494531.0,
      "end_time": 498588.0,
      "text": "with absolutely no symptoms in common,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 498588.0,
      "end_time": 501355.0,
      "text": "not even depressed moods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 501355.0,
      "end_time": 505814.0,
      "text": "can both end up with the same diagnosis of depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 505814.0,
      "end_time": 508410.0,
      "text": "For this reason especially"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 508410.0,
      "end_time": 511410.0,
      "text": "the concept of depression has been attacked"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 511410.0,
      "end_time": 516488.0,
      "text": "for being little more than a socially constructed dustbin"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 516488.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520446.00000000006,
      "text": "for all manner of human suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 520446.0,
      "end_time": 524531.0,
      "text": "Now, let us grant, as the orthodoxy has it"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 524531.0,
      "end_time": 526819.0,
      "text": "that every person inherits a certain"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 526819.0,
      "end_time": 529899.0,
      "text": "compliment of genes that make him or her"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 529899.0,
      "end_time": 532773.0,
      "text": "more or less vulnerable to developing depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 532773.0,
      "end_time": 535810.0,
      "text": "or a state that might be diagnosed as depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 535810.0,
      "end_time": 539060.0,
      "text": "during his or her lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 539060.0,
      "end_time": 540771.0,
      "text": "And let us also begin to refer"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 540771.0,
      "end_time": 543197.0,
      "text": "to this state rather than depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 543197.0,
      "end_time": 545244.0,
      "text": "as the depressive position"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 545244.0,
      "end_time": 547216.0,
      "text": "to include both clinical depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 547216.0,
      "end_time": 551651.0,
      "text": "and milder forms of depressed moods."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 551651.0,
      "end_time": 555771.0,
      "text": "A person enters the depressive position if the amount of stress"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 555771.0,
      "end_time": 559464.0,
      "text": "that he comes under is greater than"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 559464.0,
      "end_time": 562144.0,
      "text": "the amount of stress that he can tolerate"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 562144.0,
      "end_time": 566957.0,
      "text": "given the compliment of genes that he has inherited."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 566957.0,
      "end_time": 570008.0,
      "text": "Now, genes for potentially debilitating disorders"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 570008.0,
      "end_time": 573968.0,
      "text": "such as depression tend to pass out of a population"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 573968.0,
      "end_time": 577373.0,
      "text": "over time, over a very, very long period of time -"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 577373.0,
      "end_time": 579010.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re talking hundreds of generations -"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 579010.0,
      "end_time": 583116.0,
      "text": "because affected people have fewer children"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 583116.0,
      "end_time": 587848.0,
      "text": "or fewer healthy children than non-affected people."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 587848.0,
      "end_time": 591658.0,
      "text": "The fact that this has not happened for this - depression -"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 591658.0,
      "end_time": 594389.0,
      "text": "suggests that the genes are being selected for"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 594389.0,
      "end_time": 596956.0,
      "text": "despite their potentially debilitating effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 596956.0,
      "end_time": 600728.0,
      "text": "in a significant proportion of the population"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 600728.0,
      "end_time": 603117.0,
      "text": "and therefore that these genes"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 603117.0,
      "end_time": 607896.0,
      "text": "must be conferring some important adaptive advantage."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 607896.0,
      "end_time": 611710.0,
      "text": "Now, before talking about what important adaptive advantage"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 611710.0,
      "end_time": 614117.0,
      "text": "these genes could be conferring"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 614117.0,
      "end_time": 618230.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s important to note that there are other instances of genes"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 618230.0,
      "end_time": 621614.0,
      "text": "that both predispose to an illness and confer"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 621614.0,
      "end_time": 624998.0,
      "text": "an important adaptive advantage"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 624998.0,
      "end_time": 628384.0,
      "text": "and the most quoted or most studied example is usually"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 628384.0,
      "end_time": 631969.0,
      "text": "I would say sickle cell disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 631969.0,
      "end_time": 637425.0,
      "text": "In sickle cell disease, red blood cells assume a rigid sickle cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 637425.0,
      "end_time": 642292.0,
      "text": "that restricts their passage through narrow blood vessels."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 642292.0,
      "end_time": 645811.0,
      "text": "This leads to a number of serious physical complications,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 645811.0,
      "end_time": 648602.0,
      "text": "and in traditional or historical societies"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 648602.0,
      "end_time": 652885.0,
      "text": "to a radically curtailed life expectancy."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 652885.0,
      "end_time": 654484.0,
      "text": "At the same time, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 654484.0,
      "end_time": 659814.0,
      "text": "carrying just one allele of the sickle cell gene"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 659814.0,
      "end_time": 662575.0,
      "text": "prevents malarial parasites"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 662575.0,
      "end_time": 665285.0,
      "text": "from reproducing in red blood cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 665285.0,
      "end_time": 670567.0,
      "text": "and thereby confers immunity to malaria."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 670567.0,
      "end_time": 675873.0,
      "text": "The fact that the genes for sickle cell disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 675873.0,
      "end_time": 680601.0,
      "text": "are particularly common in populations from malarial regions suggests"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 680601.0,
      "end_time": 682865.0,
      "text": "that at least in evolutionary terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 682865.0,
      "end_time": 687819.0,
      "text": "a debilitating illness in the few can be a price worth paying"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 687819.0,
      "end_time": 693408.0,
      "text": "for an important adaptive advantage in the many."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 693408.0,
      "end_time": 696753.0,
      "text": "Now, what important adaptive advantage"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 696753.0,
      "end_time": 701470.0,
      "text": "could the depressive position be conferring?"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 701470.0,
      "end_time": 703821.0,
      "text": "Now if I&#39;ve made you fall asleep, I hope I haven&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 703821.0,
      "end_time": 706162.0,
      "text": "but If I have made you fall asleep then please wake up now"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 706162.0,
      "end_time": 709815.0,
      "text": "because I think this is going to be the most interesting part of my talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 709815.0,
      "end_time": 712916.0,
      "text": "So what important adaptive advantage"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 712916.0,
      "end_time": 716431.0,
      "text": "can the depressive position be conferring?"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 716431.0,
      "end_time": 720040.0,
      "text": "Just as physical pain has evolved to signal injury"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 720040.0,
      "end_time": 722311.0,
      "text": "and to prevent further injury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 722311.0,
      "end_time": 724928.0,
      "text": "so the depressive position may have evolved"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 724928.0,
      "end_time": 731897.0,
      "text": "to remove us from damaging, distressing, or futile situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 731897.0,
      "end_time": 734512.0,
      "text": "The time and space and solitude"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 734512.0,
      "end_time": 737321.0,
      "text": "that the adoption of a depressive position affords"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 737321.0,
      "end_time": 740031.0,
      "text": "prevents us from making rash decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 740031.0,
      "end_time": 742846.0,
      "text": "enables us to see the bigger picture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 742846.0,
      "end_time": 745735.0,
      "text": "and in the context of being a social animal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 745735.0,
      "end_time": 748528.0,
      "text": "to reassess our social relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 748528.0,
      "end_time": 751568.0,
      "text": "Think about those who are meaningful to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 751568.0,
      "end_time": 754092.0,
      "text": "and relate to them more meaningfully"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 754092.0,
      "end_time": 760571.0,
      "text": "and with greater compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 760571.0,
      "end_time": 763527.0,
      "text": "In other words, the depressive position may have evolved"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 763527.0,
      "end_time": 766361.0,
      "text": "as a signal that something is seriously wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 766361.0,
      "end_time": 769850.0,
      "text": "and needs working through and changing"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 769850.0,
      "end_time": 773843.0,
      "text": "or at least processing and understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 773843.0,
      "end_time": 776022.0,
      "text": "Sometimes we can become so immersed"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 776022.0,
      "end_time": 778926.0,
      "text": "in the humdrum of our everyday lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 778926.0,
      "end_time": 782720.0,
      "text": "that we no longer have time to think and feel about ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 782720.0,
      "end_time": 786769.0,
      "text": "and so lose sight of our bigger picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 786769.0,
      "end_time": 789326.0,
      "text": "The adoption of the depressive position"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 789326.0,
      "end_time": 793451.0,
      "text": "can force us to cast off the Pollyannish optimism"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 793451.0,
      "end_time": 797449.0,
      "text": "and rose-tinted spectacles that shield us from reality;"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 797449.0,
      "end_time": 799288.0,
      "text": "to take a step back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 799288.0,
      "end_time": 801769.0,
      "text": "to reevaluate our priorities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 801769.0,
      "end_time": 808769.0,
      "text": "and to formulate a realistic or the modest plan for fulfilling them."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 808769.0,
      "end_time": 812142.0,
      "text": "Now although the adoption of the depressive position"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 812142.0,
      "end_time": 815220.0,
      "text": "can fulfill what I would unfortunately call"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 815220.0,
      "end_time": 817191.0,
      "text": "such a mundane purpose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 817191.0,
      "end_time": 821711.0,
      "text": "it can also enable us to develop a more refined perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 821711.0,
      "end_time": 824767.0,
      "text": "and deeper understanding of ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 824767.0,
      "end_time": 828370.0,
      "text": "of our lives, and of life in general."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 828370.0,
      "end_time": 830476.0,
      "text": "From an existential stand point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 830476.0,
      "end_time": 832544.0,
      "text": "the adoption of the depressive position"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 832544.0,
      "end_time": 837776.0,
      "text": "obliges us to become aware of our mortality and freedom"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 837776.0,
      "end_time": 840928.0,
      "text": "and challenges us to exercise the latter"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 840928.0,
      "end_time": 844208.0,
      "text": "within the framework of the former."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 844208.0,
      "end_time": 846330.0,
      "text": "By meeting this difficult challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 846330.0,
      "end_time": 848722.0,
      "text": "we are able to break out of the mold"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 848722.0,
      "end_time": 850808.0,
      "text": "that has been imposed upon us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 850808.0,
      "end_time": 853093.0,
      "text": "discover who we truly are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 853093.0,
      "end_time": 859375.0,
      "text": "and in so doing, begin to give deep meaning to our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 859375.0,
      "end_time": 864169.0,
      "text": "Many of the most creative and insightful people in our society"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 864169.0,
      "end_time": 866888.0,
      "text": "suffer or suffered from depression"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 866888.0,
      "end_time": 871610.0,
      "text": "or a state that may or would have been diagnosed as depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 871610.0,
      "end_time": 877151.0,
      "text": "They include the politicians Winston Churchill and Abraham Lincoln."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 877151.0,
      "end_time": 881312.0,
      "text": "The poets, Charles Baudelaire, Elizabeth Bishop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 881312.0,
      "end_time": 886931.0,
      "text": "Hart Crane, Emily Dickinson, Sylvia Plath, and Rainer Maria Rilke."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 886931.0,
      "end_time": 891210.0,
      "text": "The thinkers, Michel Foucault, William James,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 891210.0,
      "end_time": 894090.0,
      "text": "John Stuart Mill, Isaac Newton,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 894090.0,
      "end_time": 897780.0,
      "text": "Friedrich Nietzsche and Arthur Schopenhauer"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 897780.0,
      "end_time": 901368.0,
      "text": "and the writers, Charles Dickens, William Faulkner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 901368.0,
      "end_time": 905293.0,
      "text": "Graham Green, Leo Tolstoy, Evelyn Waugh"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 905293.0,
      "end_time": 907171.0,
      "text": "and Tennesee Williams"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 907171.0,
      "end_time": 910929.0,
      "text": "and the list just goes on and on and on."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 910929.0,
      "end_time": 913168.0,
      "text": "To quote Marcel Proust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 913168.0,
      "end_time": 916423.0,
      "text": "who himself suffered from very severe depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 916423.0,
      "end_time": 919170.0,
      "text": "&amp;quot;Happiness is good for the body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 919170.0,
      "end_time": 926969.0,
      "text": "but it is grief which develops the strength of the mind&quot;."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 926969.0,
      "end_time": 931695.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 931695.0,
      "end_time": 934855.0,
      "text": "I take it that the clapping is for Marcel Proust."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 934855.0,
      "end_time": 939613.0,
      "text": "Now you see, people in the depressive position"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 939613.0,
      "end_time": 943273.0,
      "text": "are often stigmatized as failures or losers."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 943273.0,
      "end_time": 947250.0,
      "text": "Of course, nothing could be further from the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 947250.0,
      "end_time": 950046.0,
      "text": "If these people are in the depressive position,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 950046.0,
      "end_time": 952188.0,
      "text": "it is just because they have tried too hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 952188.0,
      "end_time": 954200.0,
      "text": "or taken on too much"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 954200.0,
      "end_time": 955730.0,
      "text": "so hard and so much"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 955730.0,
      "end_time": 959609.0,
      "text": "that they have made themselves ill with depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 959609.0,
      "end_time": 963327.0,
      "text": "In other words, if these people are in the depressive position,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 963327.0,
      "end_time": 967128.0,
      "text": "it is because their world was simply not good enough for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 967128.0,
      "end_time": 969862.0,
      "text": "They wanted more, they wanted better"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 969862.0,
      "end_time": 972685.0,
      "text": "and they wanted different."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 972685.0,
      "end_time": 977369.0,
      "text": "And not just for themselves, but for all those around them."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 977369.0,
      "end_time": 979775.0,
      "text": "So if they are failures or losers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 979775.0,
      "end_time": 983849.0,
      "text": "this is only because they&#39;ve set the bar far too high."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 983849.0,
      "end_time": 986409.0,
      "text": "They could have swept everything under the carpet"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 986409.0,
      "end_time": 989192.0,
      "text": "and pretended, as so many people do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 989192.0,
      "end_time": 992330.0,
      "text": "that all is for the best in the best of possible worlds."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 992330.0,
      "end_time": 996483.0,
      "text": "However, unlike most people, they had the strength"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 996483.0,
      "end_time": 998060.0,
      "text": "and the honesty to admit"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 998060.0,
      "end_time": 1000224.0,
      "text": "that something was amiss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1000220.0,
      "end_time": 1003599.0,
      "text": "to admit that something was not quite right."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1003600.0,
      "end_time": 1006446.0,
      "text": "So rather than being failures or losers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1006450.0,
      "end_time": 1008425.0,
      "text": "they are all the opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1008420.0,
      "end_time": 1011164.0,
      "text": "They are ambitious, they are truthful"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1011170.0,
      "end_time": 1012931.0,
      "text": "and they are courageous"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1012930.0,
      "end_time": 1017210.0,
      "text": "and that is precisely why they became ill."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1017210.0,
      "end_time": 1021125.0,
      "text": "To make them believe that they are suffering from some mental disorder"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1021120.0,
      "end_time": 1024166.0,
      "text": "or some chemical imbalance in the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1024170.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1027977.0000000001,
      "text": "and that their recovery depends entirely"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1027980.0,
      "end_time": 1031184.0,
      "text": "or even mostly on popping pills"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1031180.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1035988.0000000001,
      "text": "is to do them and to do us an immense disfavour."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1035990.0,
      "end_time": 1038051.0,
      "text": "It is to deny them the opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1038050.0,
      "end_time": 1043288.0,
      "text": "not only to identify and address important life problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1043290.0,
      "end_time": 1046117.0,
      "text": "but also to deny them the opportunity to develop"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1046109.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1048167.9999999999,
      "text": "a more refined perspective and deeper"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1048170.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1050228.0,
      "text": "understanding of themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1050230.0,
      "end_time": 1052290.0,
      "text": "and of the world around them"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1052290.0,
      "end_time": 1054809.0,
      "text": "and therefore, to deny them the opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1054810.0,
      "end_time": 1059368.0,
      "text": "to develop their highest potential as human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1059370.0,
      "end_time": 1060571.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1060570.0,
      "end_time": 1070570.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}